    <title type="short" as="introduced">Airspace Location and Enhanced Risk Transparency Act of 2026</title>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">ALERT Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To require certain aircraft to be equipped with collision mitigation technology, to improve helicopter route safety and separation around airports, to update air traffic control processes and procedures, to address national airspace system safety in Department of Defense activities, and for other purposes.</title>
